</taxonomicName>
occurs rupicolous on inselbergs surrounded by semideciduous Atlantic Forest in the state of 
<collectingRegion id="DB41F806FFB9046EEEFBFE5EFC898E87" box="[708,885,422,448]" country="Brazil" name="Espirito Santo" pageId="32" pageNumber="33">Espírito Santo</collectingRegion>
